Product Specific Transparency Statements
In our ongoing quest for transparency, Norton publishes these product and service-specific privacy notices to provide detailed information about how and why our products and services collect, process, and share your personal data. For more information about our data processing practices and any rights you may have, please see our
Global Privacy Statement
.
